name: Uncanny Persian
description: Artist: Vida V. | One of the Uncanny Canvas skull series. The original TwoToJazz piece that is transferred to this skull was a Persian calligraphy piece with made up words that but had organic and floral forms. The bright reds give it an East Asian look. TwoToJazz is an iPad app developed by Vida | Creation Date: March 3, 2021 - The calligraphy piece was created on October 7, 2014
